data.description: ATTENTION: ***HAS AN ADU*** ADU square footage is not included in the square footage of the main house.   Come see the desert meet the green oasis. This home features a beautiful soaking pond with water features, as though you are in a resort. Plush landscaping in the front yard and back yard. Intricate lighting throughout to help fit your mood and festivities. Features a legally converted garage to an ADU. This home is located south of Ventura Blvd featuring high end appliances, quartz countertops with a waterfall center island and backsplashes. Bathrooms features imported tile, vanities and finishes. Home is centrally located near award winning restaurants, shopping, wonderful schools district, local freeways. 15 minutes to the beach or Universal City. Don't miss this beautiful mid-century master piece. All the remolded features throughout this home have been fully permitted. This home wont stay on the market for long.
